  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil in an earthenware bowl over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add sliced mushrooms and cook until tender, about 4-5 minutes.",
    "Add Andouille sausage and cook, breaking it up with a spoon, until browned, about 5-6 minutes.",
    "Add bihon noodles, fish sauce, oyster sauce, and soy sauce to the bowl.",
    "Stir to combine and cook for 2-3 minutes, until noodles are well coated with the sauce.",
    "Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with chopped green onions and sesame seeds if desired."
